Use the standard library
This is how to right_angle_triangle of a and b and c:
  Remember that aa is product of a and a
  Remember that bb is product of b and b
  Remember that cc is product of c and c
  When aa is diff of cc and bb, then:
    The answer is 1
  But, if not:
    When bb is diff of cc and aa, then:
      The answer is 1
    But, if not:
      When cc is sum of aa and bb, then:
        The answer is 1
      But, if not:
        The answer is 0
      End when
    End when
  End when
